date_org: Consol. 3 Nov 1930 to take effect 16 Feb 1931
Meeting held 25 Sept 1934. Formation of C.H.S. 1 Mar 1934. Designation of dist. as Central High School District No. 3 of the Town of Hempstead, Nassau Co. 1 Mar 1934.
